quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  37,127,"Yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n alaa waﾉ擁, si wanaa fennugol mo. Awa ﾉ蓉m wonay sabu ﾉ兎 tawnoyteebe e lepte ﾉ容n."
  37,128,"Si wanaa ﾉ兎n yimﾉ兎 makko gomﾉ擁nnooﾉ兎 laﾉ橡妬ni dewe mun ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n daﾉ熔yay tawnoyeede e lepte ﾉ容n."
  37,129,"Men accani mo mantoore e jantoore labaande, e mofte sakkitiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  37,130,"Alla hiwrike mantii Ilyaasna'en."
  37,131,"Ko wano Men yoﾉ妬tiri non Ilyaasa'en, woni ko Men yoﾉ妬tirta jeyaaﾉ兎 Amen gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  37,132,"Kanko Ilyaasa, ko o jeyanooﾉ熔 e jeyaaﾉ兎 Amen gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 goongini gomﾉ擁ngol Joomi mun."
  37,133,"Pellet, Luutu kadi, ko jeyanooﾉ熔 e Nulaaﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎n nuliranooﾉ兎 e yimﾉ兎 mun, wewlingol e jertingol."
  37,134,"Janto nde Men daﾉ溶dunoo mo, kanko e ﾉ兎ynguure makko nden fow, e lepte wurtanooﾉ容 e yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n."
  37,135,"Si wanaa debbo makko on, on jeyano e yimﾉ兎 makko leptaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n; tawde ko o yedunooﾉ熔."
  37,136,"Refti Men halki fennunooﾉ兎 mo, heddii ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  37,137,"Onon yimﾉ兎 Makkah ﾉ兎n non, hiﾉ熔n rewa e galleeji maﾉ橡兎, tuma setorton Saami, e dawol mon."
  37,138,"Hiﾉ熔n rewa e hoore-maﾉ橡兎 kadi, ka jemma. E on haqqiltaa, waajitoron ko heﾉ妬 ﾉ兎 kon, ﾉ殿awo ﾉ兎 fennude ﾉ兎 yedda ﾉ兎 faggitoo bonunnda mo adaaka e mun?"
  37,139,"Pellet, Yuunusa kadi, ko jeyanooﾉ熔 e Nulaaﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎n nuliranooﾉ兎 e yimﾉ兎 mun, wewlingol e jertingol."
  37,140,"Janto nde o dogunoo yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n, ko aldaa e duﾅ蟻yee Joomi makko. O waﾉ遼熔yii laana hebbiniraaka yimﾉ兎 e dolle."
  37,141,"Laana kan eﾉ橡妬 yoolagol, hakkee ko ka heewi. ﾆ‘ urbinii nder ton, ndaarugol ko homﾉ兎 gasetee bugedee ka maayo, fii ﾉ蓉ytugol teddeendi makka ndin; Yuunusa jeyaa e ﾉ兎n foolaaﾉ兎 ka urba, ﾉ兎 bugii mo ka maayo."
  37,142,"Nde ﾉ兎 buginoo mo ka maayo, linngii ngii moﾉ擁 mo, fewndo ka o felnii; tawde o yehii ka maayo, o duﾅ喫naaki e Joomi makko."
  37,143,"Si wanaano tawde Yuunusa ko jeyanooﾉ熔 e jantotooﾉ兎 Alla ko ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁, si wanaano subbunhinagol makko ngol ka nder reedu lingii ngii"
  37,144,"O ﾃｱiiﾉ殿yno ka reedu lingii ngii, haa ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, ﾉ熔n wona yenaande makko."
  37,145,"Men sorti mo e reedu lingii ngii, Men werlii mo ka ladde, ko o lo'uﾉ熔, battane ko o ﾉ登oyi kon ka reedu maggii."
  37,146,"Men fuﾉ擁nani mo e e ladde yeewnde nde, leggal buudi, ka o ﾉ蓉wora o ﾃｱaama."
  37,147,"Men nuli mo e yimﾉ兎 makko hawraynooﾉ兎: ujune teemedere maa ﾉ砥ri ﾉ兎."
  37,148,"ﾆ‘ gomﾉ擁ni mo, ﾉ兎 goongini ko o addi kon, Alla dakmiti ﾉ兎 e nguurndam maﾉ橡兎 aduna ﾉ預m, haa dumunna maﾉ橡兎 on timmi."
  37,149,"Muhammad, lamndorii ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎 "ﾅ喫ﾃｱugol": E on waﾉ預nay Alla ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 rewﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 aﾃｱanﾉ熔n hoore-mon, heertinanon ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fii mon? Ko honﾉ蓉m e senndoore nii?"
  37,150,"Ko honno ﾉ兎 aaﾆｴorta wonnde Malaa'ika'en ko rewﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 tawanooka tageede majji, ﾉ兎 seeditaaki ﾉ蓉m?"
  37,151,"Pellet sirkuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 e pennugol mum en e fepindaade ﾉ兎 penaale e dow Alla ﾉ兎 ngaskina ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 e dow Makko, ﾉ兎 ko fenooﾉ兎 e koﾉ兎 noddittoo ko."
  37,152,"37:151"
  37,153,"Hara Allah suﾉ殿n hoore Makko, ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 rewﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 aﾃｱanﾉ熔n hoore-mon, e dow ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 yiﾉ預nﾉ熔n hoore-mon ﾉ兎n? Kallaa! wanaa non!"